des:
Questions about, on which team is a certain player chosen at random playing, this 2019 season.
It consists of five questions, which will have 4 possible answers, the user will answer with the number associated with the answer that he thinks is correct.
In case of not getting it right, it will be said which was the correct answer.
If it is necessary to repeat the question, the user can say (repeat question).
In the end they will tell the successes that have been.
Possible updates of the equipment in the winter and summer markets will be taken into account with an update.
